commit.message:
refactor(temp-mail): rename gptmail refs to temp_mail across core modules

- controllers/accounts: _handle_gptmail_import -> _handle_temp_mail_import;
  strict import via temp_mail_service.import_user_mailbox;
  _detect_line_type returns type=temp_mail/provider=temp_mail for 1-part lines;
  export text labels updated; code formatting cleanup (black-style)
- controllers/emails: api_external_get_probe_status handles cancelled probe (409)
- controllers/system: use ensure_external_email_scope instead of
  ensure_external_email_access for external account status
- services/__init__: update docstring to drop GPTMail mention
- services/providers: add temp_mail key to PROVIDER_GROUP_NAME
- services/temp_email_content: update comment (legacy bridge doc reference)
